original_title: TNA One Night Only: Joker's Wild 3
overview: 30 men and 2 Knockouts compete in a tournament for $100,000. It is made up of tag team matches in which the partners are randomly drawn in a lottery and teams will work together to advance to the main event Battle Royal, with the grand prize of US$100,000. It took place on February 14, 2015, from the Impact Zone at Universal Studios in Orlando, Florida, and was shown on PPV on March 6, 2015.
title: TNA One Night Only: Joker's Wild 3
